# The initial value for number will be 5, since that is the first element of the list
</input></program>
        <p>Termination condition: When we have finished processing the last element of the list (2)</p>
        <p>Body that is repeated based on indentation:</p>
        <program language="python"><input>
total = total + number
</input></program>
